274
00:15:59,866 --> 00:16:01,958
Quem falou em barris?

275
00:16:01,989 --> 00:16:06,128
Refiro-me a um oceano da coisa.

276
00:16:14,246 --> 00:16:16,250
Dá-lhe um minuto, sim?

277
00:16:16,732 --> 00:16:17,920
Confia nele.

278
00:16:18,744 --> 00:16:20,020
"Confia nele".

279
00:16:20,309 --> 00:16:21,328
Meu Deus.

280
00:16:24,761 --> 00:16:26,355
Bem...

281
00:16:27,062 --> 00:16:28,131
estou à espera.

282
00:16:28,161 --> 00:16:32,618
